@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Us";
}

<h2>About Us</h2>

<style>
    .about-container {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
        border: 1px solid #ddd;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }

    .about h2 {
        color: #333;
        font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .about p {
        color: #555;
        font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .about p strong {
        color: #222;
    }
</style>

<div class="about-container">
    <p class="about">
        <strong>A Legacy of Quality Craftsmanship</strong><br>
        Established with a passion for furniture craftsmanship and timeless design, Spring Furniture has been a trusted name since [year of establishment].
    </p>
    <p class="about">
        Today, Spring Furniture is dedicated to providing exquisite furniture pieces that elevate homes and inspire lifestyles. Our commitment to quality and customer satisfaction has made us a preferred choice for [mention your customer base or market].
    </p>
    <p class="about">
        <strong>Designed for Comfort and Style</strong><br>
        Based in [city/state/country], Spring Furniture combines traditional craftsmanship with modern aesthetics to create furniture that enhances every room's ambiance.
    </p>
    <p class="about">
        <strong>Our Commitment to Sustainability</strong><br>
        At Spring Furniture, sustainability is at the heart of what we do. We prioritize environmentally friendly practices and materials to ensure our furniture not only beautifies your space but also respects our planet.
    </p>
    <p class="about">
        <strong>Visit Us</strong><br>
        Explore our collection of sofas, dining sets, bedroom furniture, and more. Experience the Spring Furniture difference and transform your house into a home.
    </p>
</div>
